
in first terminal, run:

 - virtualenv ve
 - source ve/bin/activate
 - pip install radical.pilot
 - pip install bottle
 - python emgr-rest.py 

in second terminal, run commands like:

curl -X GET    http://localhost:8080/executions/
curl -X PUT    http://localhost:8080/executions/ --data-urlencode "json=config.json"
curl -X GET    http://localhost:8080/executions/execution.016631.0005
curl -X GET    http://localhost:8080/executions/
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:8080/executions/execution.016631.0005
curl -X GET    http://localhost:8080/executions/

